{"tid":1085713,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"裸男將軍澳商場遊逛偷衫襲警 涉三宗罪被捕","createTime":"2019-03-31T11:02:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-31T11:25:08.000Z","uid":51620,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d5e7305fe27ffbedf28e85608b4d205a3c50c141","tid":1085713,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T11:02:13.000Z","msg":"將軍澳新都城中心今早上演一幕春光無限奇景！早上約10時，一名全裸男無懼眾人目光，在新都城中心商場閒逛，只見他旁若無人，坦蕩蕩在商場遊花園。其間他走進一間專賣年輕少女款式的內衣及優閒衣服的店舖，偷去3件衣服，職員發現報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n警員接報到場欲拘捕這名裸男，裸男竟揮拳毆打警員，其後同袍合力將裸男制服，警方經初步調查，姓林（41歲）裸男，懷疑在上址店鋪盜取三件合共約值350元的衣服。林涉嫌猥褻露體、盜竊及襲警被捕，案件交由將軍澳警區刑事調查隊第四隊跟進。該名警員面及腳受傷，清醒送院治理。據悉，被捕人有精神病紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190331/small/1554020262_c6fe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190331%2Fsmall%2F1554020262_c6fe.jpg&h=d31cf764&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190331/59433545?fbclid=IwAR24NbZHf0S3QXjCAuL2OrUAG2bW4pEP8iqAMSjkgyXbv5dPZWM0eZ3OEMQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190331%2F59433545%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR24NbZHf0S3QXjCAuL2OrUAG2bW4pEP8iqAMSjkgyXbv5dPZWM0eZ3OEMQ&d=Sk6y7wLkZ8LsH37jlkaP90UPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=f61e594e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190331%2F59433545%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR24NbZHf0S3QXjCAuL2OrUAG2bW4pEP8iqAMSjkgyXbv5dPZWM0eZ3OEMQ&h=c366e19e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190331/59433545?fbclid=IwAR24NbZHf0S3QXjCAuL2OrUAG2bW4pEP8iqAMSjkgyXbv5dPZWM0eZ3OEMQ</a>"},{"pid":"4dc06e5b5571e4238b5c04b9f633883cc782a446","tid":1085713,"uid":34779,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T11:13:14.000Z","msg":"Terminator"},{"pid":"8e69c7f043cb9c5493e208a4237cb190c44573b4","tid":1085713,"uid":112747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T11:18:59.000Z","msg":"正面呢"},{"pid":"ea1f9325faec9e953f0aecf396b0fb10600c3b14","tid":1085713,"uid":73628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-31T11:25:08.000Z","msg":"正面無碼圖呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}